OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fthickening through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight. Winds also strengthening,
OL,8,Fwith upland gales likely, and perhaps
OL,9,Fsome rain for a time. Staying mild,
OL,10,Fand frost free.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FWindy, with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain becoming more frequent through
OL,14,Fthe morning. Occasionally heavy and
OL,15,Fblustery rain then moves southeast
OL,16,Fearly afternoon. Brighter, colder
OL,17,Fweather follows through the evening,
OL,18,Fwith showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
